'''The Hub''' was a massive computer complex built by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] under [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] orders to coordinate the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. It was decided it was too risky to be held on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], and so was constructed in [[Pyramid One]] on [[Ahakista/Legends|Ahakista]]. In [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]] [[Raze (criminal)|Raze]] assembled a team under [[Wyl Tarson]] to destroy it; however the plot was foiled.

